By Chibuike Nwabuko Abuja {Sundiata Post} – Senator Ben Murray Bruce has informed that he was in touch with the US, US and EU this morning to get the Visa of Senator Godswill Akpabio and his gang members revoked so that they will not be able to travel abroad but to remain in Nigeria. The common sense senator said that by the time that is done, Akpabio’s jet will be grounded and then he will contribute money with his friends and buy donkey for him to use. The senator recalled that there is now good hospital in Bayelsa for people to access medical health rather than travelling abroad. Recall that there is speculations that Senator Godswill Akpabio is rumoured to be defecting to the APC for a juicy position in the red chamber. Details Later…. 